					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This article gives away the punchline before the joke actually starts. The second sentence is the same as the final sentence, which just <em>ruins</em> the joke. It's not unexpected, but the opposite: I'm expecting it the entire time I'm reading.</p> <p>Also, that variant rating module is broken as fuck on this theme. Immediate downvote for that.</p> 
				 	]]>
