				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12502071/spc-3787#post-4354778</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2019 19:49:47 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This article poses two questions: &quot;What if horses could punch sharks?&quot; and &quot;What if horses were afraid of sharks?&quot;. These questions make very little sense to begin with, but for some reason, that's what makes it <em>all the more hilarious</em>. Only the Centre would try something so ridiculous!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
